  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Element</strong>&nbsp;universal;&nbsp;<strong>Type</strong>&nbsp;form infusion;&nbsp;<strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;2;&nbsp;<strong>Burn</strong>&nbsp;2<br><strong>Prerequisite</strong>&nbsp;kinetic blade<br><strong>Associated Blasts</strong>&nbsp;any<br><strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;none</p>\n<p>You use your element’s power to instantly move 30 feet in any direction (even straight up), manifest a kinetic blade, and attack once. You gain a +2 bonus on the attack roll and take a –2 penalty to your AC until the start of your next turn. The movement doesn’t provoke attacks of opportunity, though activating blade rush does.</p>\n<p>If you have the kinetic whip infusion, you can manifest a kinetic whip instead of a kinetic blade at the end of your movement by increasing the burn cost of this infusion by 1.</p>\n<p>The blade or whip vanishes instantly after the rush.</p>",
